Which one is your favorite, from 1 to 10? 💙

1. Zakynthos @mixtita
2. Ithaca @giannistsou.1
3. Ikaria @giannistsou.1
4. Koufonisia @stef_greece
5. Kefalonia @mixtita
6. Paxoi @minogiannisvalantis
7. Crete @stef_greece
8. Milos @stef_greece
9. Antipaxos @giannistsou.1
10. Lefkada @minogiannisvalantis
